OL,3,CCraig Williams loses Montgomeryshire &
OL,4,CGlyndwr seat after betting scandal
OL,6,FLabour has gained Montgomeryshire and
OL,7,FGlyndwr from the Conservatives, with
OL,8,FCraig Williams losing his seat after a
OL,9,Fbetting scandal.
OL,11,FLabour's Steve Witherden has been
OL,12,Felected, with Reform taking the second
OL,13,Flargest share of the vote.
OL,15,FThe Conservative Party had withdrawn
OL,16,Fits support for Williams after he was
OL,17,Fcaught up in allegations of betting on
OL,18,Fthe date of the timing of the UK
OL,19,FGeneral Election before it was
OL,20,Fannounced.
