OL,3,CCraig Williams loses Montgomeryshire &
OL,4,CGlyndwr seat after betting scandal
OL,6,FWilliams was Rishi Sunak's
OL,7,FParliamentary Private Secretary (PPS),
OL,8,Fmeaning that he was one of the former
OL,9,Fprime minister's closest aides.
OL,11,FHe admitted making a "huge error of
OL,12,Fjudgement" in placing the bet on the
OL,13,Fdate of the election days before it
OL,14,Fwas officially announced, with the
OL,15,FGambling Commission launching a probe.
