OL,3,CCraig Williams loses Montgomeryshire &
OL,4,CGlyndwr seat after betting scandal
OL,6,FIn a video posted on X, formerly
OL,7,FTwitter, ahead of the July 4 election,
OL,8,FMr Williams said: "I just want (to
OL,9,Fsend) a quick message to the
OL,10,Fconstituents of Montgomeryshire and
OL,11,FGlyndwr: I remain on the ballot paper
OL,12,Fand on 4th July and I hope to secure
OL,13,Fyour support after years of delivery.
OL,15,F"I committed an error of judgement,
OL,16,Fnot an offence, and I want to
OL,17,Freiterate my apology directly to you.
OL,19,F"I'm fully co-operating with routine
OL,20,Finquiries by the Gambling Commission
OL,21,Fand I intend to clear my name.
